    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This specialized <ref refid="classOpFunc" kindref="compound">OpFunc</ref> is for returning a single field value It generates an opFunc that takes a single argument, a reference to a vector into which the return value should be appended. It manages the &apos;get&apos; function that retrieves the return value. Note that the &apos;get&apos; function must be blocking in case the request goes off node. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
